'''瓦茨拉夫·哈维尔创意异议人士奖'''（{{lang-en|Václav Havel Prize for Creative Dissent}}）是总部位于[[美国|美国]][[纽约|纽约]]的{{le|人权基金会|Human Rights Foundation}}于2012年起颁发的奖项，以奖励“用勇气和创意挑战不公、生活在真实中的创意异议人士”。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://humanrightsfoundation.org/news/the-vaclav-havel-prize-for-creative-dissent-0069 |title=The Václav Havel Prize for Creative Dissent |date=11 April 2012 |publisher=Human Rights Foundation |accessdate=1 August 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140517182232/http://humanrightsfoundation.org/news/the-vaclav-havel-prize-for-creative-dissent-0069 |archive-date=2014-05-17 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

该奖项是为纪念原[[捷克|捷克]]异议作家、首任[[捷克总统|捷克总统]][[瓦茨拉夫·哈维尔|瓦茨拉夫·哈维尔]]而于其逝世后次年设立的，设立过程中还得到了哈维尔遗霜[[达格玛·哈维尔|达格玛·哈维尔]]相助。<ref name=HP>{{cite web |url=http://www.havelprize.org/ |title=Inaugural Václav Havel Prize for Creative Dissent awarded to Ai Weiwei, Manal al-Sharif, and Aung San Suu Kyi |date=2 May 2012 |publisher=HavelPrize.org |accessdate=16 May 2012 |archive-date=2012-05-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120508111207/http://www.havelprize.org/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[Google|Google]]共同创始人[[谢尔盖·布林|谢尔盖·布林]]与[[Paypal|Paypal]]共同创始人[[彼得·蒂尔|彼得·蒂尔]]为该奖项提供了部分资金。<ref name=WSJ>{{cite web |url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052702304203604577396372334739162.html |title=A Prize for Creative Dissent |date=13 May 2012 |work=The Wall Street Journal |accessdate=16 May 2012 |archive-date=2013-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130512105705/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052702304203604577396372334739162.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

